CELEBRATING 40 YEARS OF SERVICE
Since 1975, we have been committed to providing top quality products, competitive pricing, and unequaled service to our customers.
HARCO, INC. supplies underground water and sewer materials such as pipe, valves, fittings, fire hydrants, trench drains, and many related products, as well as the most complete line of industrial and commercial insulation products in the area. 
 Our unique combination of product lines along with our product knowledge and dedication to
                  customer service makes HARCO the ideal choice for contractors, municipalities and both
                  commercial and industrial facilities.
For inquiries and additional information, please call us toll free at 800-366-5876, local 502-366-4596 or fax us at 502-366-3739.

 
We stock Waterous and American Darling fire hydrants.









 

