Harco LLC/CT: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback























harco llc/ct
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Industrials
Industry: Aerospace & Defense
Sub-Industry: Aircraft & Parts
Harco LLC of Connecticut designs and manufactures aircraft parts. The Company offers air data systems, on-engine and airframe electrical cable assemblies, and gas turbine high temperature and other advanced sensor products. Harco serves customers worldwide.




