Paint Projects Don't Have To Be Messy!










Clean Up Made Easy!Safe for hands and any surface








Absorb and Lock DesignSmear-Free clean-up








Powerful on Tools and SpillsSafe on skin!
















clean up made easy!
SAFE FOR HANDS AND ANY SURFACE



SEE MIRACLEWIPES IN ACTION!








MiracleWipes for Surfaces




MiracleWipes for Hands




MiracleWipes for Tools




DISCOVER MORE!










CLEAN UP MADE EASY


MiracleWipes Paint offers Do-It-Yourself and Professional Painters quick and convenient cleanup for hands, surfaces and tools. MiracleWipes also provide additional benefits as it also acts as a surface prep wipe for walls, baseboards, furniture, cabinets and more.



Ideal for paint preparation, paint clean up, tool cleaning and hand cleaning



Safe, yet exceptionally powerful when compared to traditional solvents and cleaning products



Removes dirt, grease, and grime to ensure an even application of paint



Clean surfaces and tools after application to absorb and lock in contaminants like uncured paint and more



Safe to use on all painted surfaces, plastic, metal, porcelain, ceramic, cement, hands and skin










AVailable atSherwin-Williams














AmazingLYclean!


Absorb and Lock Design - Smear-Free Clean-up MiracleWipes Technology quickly loosens paint, and sucks it into a central layer, preventing smears. Holds 6X its weight in oil and contaminants.









